text: Phryganeidae is a family of giant casemakers in the order Trichoptera. There are about 16 genera and at least 80 described species in Phryganeidae. The type genus for Phryganeidae is Phryganea C. Linnaeus, 1758. ==Genera== ==References== ==Further reading== * * * * * * * * Category:Trichoptera families
